name: Is This the End?
description: I don't belong here. Where am I? What is this? Why this rounded thing's glowing? And what am I gonna do when I know what the hell is this? Do I need to destroy it or just leave it behind like nothing was happen? So many questions that I don't know if there's any "right answer". So many that I can't even remember where do I came from. // 3100px x 3100px 300 DPI (8.206.676 bytes)
